BICEPS WORKOUT (45–60 min)
1️⃣ Barbell Curl (Main mass builder)
Weight: Start 10–15 kg (including bar)
Sets/Reps: 3 sets × 8–12 reps
How to do:
Stand straight, feet shoulder-width
Grip bar shoulder-width, palms up
Curl up slowly till chest level
Squeeze biceps 1 sec
Lower slowly (2–3 sec)

45+ Pushups means biological age is 18 for men
